## Korean translations for chrome layouts (top-nav, mobile-nav, footer,
## flash group, theme toggle). Strings here are visible on every page,
## so consistency with the auth + dashboard surfaces matters.
##
## #. TODO native-speaker review — anchors:
##   - "워크스페이스" (workspace) is the chosen user-facing label per
##     SPEC.md Document-pivot; "안건" / "사건" are no longer surfaced.
##   - "스튜디오" (Studio) stays English-romanised — it's the product's
##     own internal name for the editor surface, not a generic word.
##   - "법무 문서" (legal document) over "법률 문서" — more colloquial
##     for solo/in-house lawyers per the design brief.
